jasperReport.queryString: SELECT "Date", "Time", "DischargeDate", "DischargeTime", "HN", "VN", "Patient", "ReceiveDate", "ReceiveTime", "ReceiptNo", "รวมค่าบริการBILLED", "ส่วนลด", "ส่วนลดพิเศษ", "ส่วนลดปัดเศษ", "สุทธิ", "สิทธิการรักษาทั้งหมด" FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT accdebit.visit_date "Date", accdebit.visit_time "Time", accdebit.financial_discharge_date "DischargeDate", accdebit.financial_discharge_time "DischargeTime", accdebit.hn "HN", accdebit.vn "VN", accdebit.patient_name "Patient", accdebit.receive_date "ReceiveDate", accdebit.receive_time "ReceiveTime", accdebit.receipt_number "ReceiptNo", sale "รวมค่าบริการBILLED", discount "ส่วนลด", special_discount "ส่วนลดพิเศษ", decimal_discount "ส่วนลดปัดเศษ", paid "สุทธิ", accdebit.all_plan "สิทธิการรักษาทั้งหมด", acccredit.acccredit_visit_id FROM bpk_account_debit_detail accdebit LEFT JOIN ( SELECT DISTINCT visit_id AS acccredit_visit_id FROM bpk_account_credit_detail WHERE verify_date='$P!{dBeginDate}' ) acccredit ON acccredit.acccredit_visit_id=accdebit.visit_id AND accdebit.receive_date='$P!{dBeginDate}' WHERE accdebit.receive_date='$P!{dBeginDate}' AND accdebit.fix_visit_type_id='0' ) tmp WHERE tmp.acccredit_visit_id IS NULL ORDER BY tmp."ReceiveDate", tmp."ReceiveTime", tmp."Date", tmp."Time"
